acity%20to%20make%20as%20much%20as%20%2445%20billion%20in%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20ready%20to%20increase%20our%20production.%20We%20have%20the%20capacity%20to%20increase%20our%20production%2C%26quot%3B%20Goncharov%20said.%20But%20for%20now%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20still%20work%20in%20the%20limit%20of%20the%20budget%20of%20Ukraine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20men%20work%20on%20drone%20components%20over%20a%20wooden%20table%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67daad3c69253ccddf99a963%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221334%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMen%20work%20at%20a%20factory%20producing%20drones%20for%20the%20Ukrainian%20Armed%20Forces%20in%20Kyiv%2C%20Ukraine.%3Cp%3EVitalii%20Nosach%2FGlobal%20Images%20Ukraine%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGovernment%20officials%20have%20shared%20similar%20observations.%20For%20instance%2C%20Oleksandr%20Kamyshin%2C%20then%20Ukraine's%20minister%20of%20strategic%20industries%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pravda.com.ua%2Feng%2Fnews%2F2024%2F04%2F15%2F7451294%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20April%202024%20that%20Ukraine's%20defense%20production%20capacity%20was%20three%20times%20as%20much%20as%20its%20defense%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIhor%20Fedirko%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20the%20Ukrainian%20Council%20of%20Defence%20Industry%2C%20a%20body%20that%20represents%20more%20than%20100%20companies%2C%20told%20BI%20%26quot%3Bthere%20are%20huge%20spare%20manufacturing%20capacities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20defense%20companies%20typically%20rely%20on%20money%20from%20the%20government%20buying%20their%20goods%20for%20the%20military.%20Units%20also%20buy%20some%20weaponry%20and%20items%20themselves%2C%20but%20that%20practice%20doesn't%20add%20up%20to%20the%20same%20scale%20or%20offer%20businesses%20the%20same%20confidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%