aterials%20used%20or%20movement%20mechanisms%2C%20a%20lot%20more%20interesting%2C%20regardless%20of%20how%20luxurious%20the%20watch%20is.%C2%A0The%20best%20way%20to%20learn%20about%20watches%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20through%C2%A0forums%2C%20meetups%2C%20and%20online%20resources%20like%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2F5513mattedial.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E5513mattedial.com%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0or%20larger%20publications%20such%20as%20Hodinkee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPetronzi%20said%20that%20once%20you%20start%20with%20a%20%24200%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbusiness-owner-bought-luxury-rolex-watch-status-symbol-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewatch%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20you%20can%20wear%20it%20and%20enjoy%20it%20while%20also%20looking%20ahead%20to%20the%20next%20purchase%20and%20putting%20money%20aside%20into%20a%20watch%20wealth%20fund.%20Once%20you%20have%20another%20%24300%20saved%20up%2C%20you%20can%20sell%20the%20original%20watch%2C%20and%20now%20you'll%20have%20%24500%20to%20go%20toward%20a%20new%20watch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20purchase%20well%2C%20you%20might%20even%20make%20money%20off%20the%20watch%20you%20sell%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20do%20that%20enough%20times%20and%20before%20you%20know%20it%2C%20you%20have%20a%20several-thousand-dollar%20watch%2C%20but%20you%20didn't%20actually%20spend%20several%20thousand%20dollars%20because%20you%20just%20rolled%20it%20into%20that%20watch%20from%20your%20previous%20sale%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cb268025-5ea0-4278-9003-ccf5c3c90328%5C%22%3EThe%20'Snowball%20Approach'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPetronzi%20said%20the%20watch%20he%20had%20in%20grad%20school%20was%20a%20Rolex%20Submariner%205513%20and%20that%20it%20wasn't%20loud%20or%20flashy%3B%20it%20was%20just%20a%20piece%20he%20loved%20and%20found%20interesting.%20He%20also%20said%20he%20would%20not%20have%20been%20able%20to%20afford%20it%20had%20he%20not%20been%20