he%20questions%20being%20used%20to%20train%20AI%20voice%20models%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-wont-rule-out-merging-xai-tesla-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%E2%80%99s%20xAI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20alongside%20everyday%20topics%20about%20DIY%20plumbing%20and%20trip%20planning%2C%20documents%20obtained%20by%20Business%20Insider%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFreelancers%20for%20data-labeling%20company%20Scale%20AI%20are%20being%20paid%20to%20record%20conversations%20with%20other%20contractors%20about%20things%20like%20colonizing%20Mars%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-spacex-plan-colonize-mars-dont-count-on-it-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20goal%20of%20Musk%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20superheroes%2C%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20make%20xAI%E2%80%99s%20voice%20models%20sound%20less%20like%20a%20robot%20and%20more%20like%20a%20real%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20April%2C%20Scale%20AI%20was%20running%20at%20least%2010%20generative%20AI%20projects%20for%20xAI%2C%20according%20to%20an%20internal%20dashboard%20seen%20by%20BI.%20The%20dashboard%20lists%20over%20100%20AI%20training%20projects%20for%20xAI%20and%20other%20clients%2C%20including%20Apple%2C%20Google%20DeepMind%2C%20and%20Meta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScale%20AI%E2%80%99s%20work%20comes%20as%20companies%20across%20the%20industry%20are%20pushing%20to%20make%20their%20bots%20more%20conversational%20and%20human-like%20to%20help%20compete%20for%20users%20who%20might%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-google-gemini-advanced-ultra-ai-chatbot-cost-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epay%20for%20their%20premium%20versions%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScale%20AI%20and%20xAI%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2249a2b448-c5e2-42a4-991c-0f2d0e8c8320%5C%22%3EInside%20%E2%80%98Project%20Xylophone%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20obtained%20four%20Scale%20AI%20documents%20%E2%80%94%20two%20sets%20of%20project%20instructions%2C%20a%20set%20of%20instructions%20for%20reviewers%20who%20check%20submissions%2C%20and%20a%20conversation%20topic%20guide%20%E2%80%94%20that%20outline%20how%20%E2%80%9CProject%20Xylophone%E2%80%9D%20works%20for%20xAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20documents%20do%20not%20state%20which%20xAI%20model%20is%20being%20trained.%20In%20late%20February%2C%20Musk%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1893506728710566302%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20beta%20rollout%20of%20a%20voice%20mode%20for%20Grok%2C%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20only%20publicly%20known%20AI%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Scale%20AI%20project%20dashboard%20shows%20contractors%20working%20on%20Project%20Xylophone%20are%20asked%20to%20record%20short%20conversations%2C%20focusing%20on%20%E2%80%9Caudio%20quality%20and%20natural%20fluency.%E2%80%9D%20They%20are%20especially%20encouraged%20to%20join%20if%20they%20have%20experience%20with%20voice%20acting.%20The%20dashboard%20says%20the%20project%20is%20aiming%20for%20%E2%80%9Cengaging%20scripts%2C%20great%20voice%20acting%2C%20and%20high%20quality%20audio.%E2%80%9D%20Scale%E2%80%99s%20dashboard%20is%20not%20accessible%20to%20contractors%2C%20who%20may%20not%20know%20who%20the%20client%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Project%20Xylophone%2C%20gig%20workers%20located%20around%20the%20world%20can%20pick%20from%20hundreds%20of%20conversation%20topics%20about%20ethics%2C%20philosophy%2C%20business%2C%20and%20travel%2C%20and%20record%20answers%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20languages%20for%20a%20few%20dollars%20per%20task.%20It%20splits%20the%20work%20between%20an%20invite-only%20project%20called%20%E2%80%9CConversations%2C%E2%80%9D%20which%20gig%20workers%20do%20in%20three-person%20teams%2C%20and%20%E2%80%9CGrasslands%2C%E2%80%9D%20which%20they%20do%20solo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CConversations%E2%80%9D%20teams%20are%20asked%20to%20set%20up%20realistic%20conversations%20with%20each%20other%20over%20Zoom.%20Contributors%20take%20turns%20asking%20questions%20from%20a%20prompt%20spreadsheet%2C%20which%20was%20active%20earlier%20this%20week.%20The%20sheet%20includes%20more%20than%20700%20conversation%20starters%20on%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20topics%2C%20including%20postapocalyptic%20survival%20tactics%2C%20planning%20trips%20to%20India%2C%20and%20managing%20anxiety%20and%20panic%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20were%20designing%20the%20'culture'%20for%20the%20first%20Mars%20settlement%2C%20what%20Earth%20tradition%20would%20you%20definitely%20want%20to%20recreate%2C%20and%20what%20would%20you%20be%20excited%20to%20leave%20behind%20forever%3F%E2%80%9D%20reads%20one%20prompt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20found%20that%20about%2010%25%20of%20the%20conversation%20prompts%20in%20the%20document%20we%20reviewed%20are%20science%20fiction-related.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ctable%3E%3Ccolgroup%3E%3Ccol%3E%3C%2Fcolgroup%3E%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Cstrong%3EExamples%20of%20suggested%20conversation%20starters%20from%20the%20Scale%20AI%20documents%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3EWhat's%20a%20'villain'%20in%20your%20daily%20life%20that%20you%20wish%20a%20superhero%20team%20could%20swoop%20in%20and%20fix%20for%20everyone%3F%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3EIf%20the%20zombie%20apocalypse%20hit%20tomorrow%2C%20what's%20the%20first%20thing%20you'd%20grab%20from%20your%20house%20before%20making%20a%20run%20for%20it%3F%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3EImagine%20you're%20the%20mission%20psychologist%20for%20a%20Mars%20colony%E2%80%94what%20personality%20type%20or%20quirky%20trait%20would%20you%20secretly%20hope%20to%20find%20in%20your%20fellow%20colonists%3F%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3EWhat's%20the%20most%20memorable%20plumbing%20disaster%20you've%20experienced%20as%20a%20homeowner%E2%80%94and%20did%20you%20try%20to%20fix%20it%20yourself%20or%20immediately%20call%20for%20help%3F%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3EDo%20you%20remember%20the%20first%20time%20you%20had%20to%20ask%20for%20more%20money%20or%20better%20benefits%3F%20What%20was%20going%20through%20your%20head%3F%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20questions%20are%20about%20the%20US%20political%20and%20judiciary%20systems%2C%20but%20the%20set%20does%20not%20include%20hot-button%20political%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20%E2%80%9CConversation%E2%80%9D%20arm%2C%20instructions%20for%20%E2%80%9Cgood%E2%80%9D%20conversations%20are%20explicit%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20recording%20must%20sound%20extremely%20natural%2C%20as%20if%20you%20were%20having%20a%20casual%20conversation%20with%20a%20friend.%20This%20includes%20being%20emotional%2C%20having%20varied%20intonations%2C%20and%20interrupting%20each%20other!%20Please%20avoid%20sounding%20like%20an%20interview.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20%E2%80%9CGrasslands%E2%80%9D%20arm%2C%20solo%20workers%20are%20asked%20to%20create%20unscripted%2C%20natural-sounding%20recordings%20in%20their%20native%20language.%20Each%20worker%20is%20given%20a%20conversation%20type%20and%20subcategory%2C%20and%20is%20told%20to%20let%20the%20conversation%20flow%2C%20in%20any%20setting%20they%20like%2C%20with%20background%20noise%20encouraged.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20dozens%20of%20subcategories%2C%20like%20%E2%80%9CSocratic%20questioning%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Creflective%20storytelling%2C%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9Ccourtly%20love%20scenarios%2C%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9Chero-villain%20confrontations%2C%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9Ccollaborative%20puzzle-solving%2C%E2%80%9D%20sometimes%20with%20different%20accents%2C%20sound%20effects%2C%20or%20invented%20linguistic%20patterns%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f7456d26-decd-401d-b239-bf9c0c3f89f8%5C%22%3EFast%20and%20accurate%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20Scale%20AI%20contractors%2C%20who%20asked%20not%20to%20be%20named%20because%20they%20signed%20nondisclosure%20agreements%2C%20said%20that%20projects%20are%20assigned%20to%20contractors%20based%20on%20their%20skill%20sets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20of%20the%20contractors%20said%20that%20payment%20for%20the%20Grassland%20project%2C%20which%20was%20assigned%20to%20contractors%20based%20on%20their%20location%20and%20language%20expertise%2C%20started%20with%20%243%20per%20task%2C%20and%20was%20cut%20to%20%241%20per%20task%20roughly%20a%20month%20later.%20Contractors%20have%20five%20minutes%20to%20complete%20each%20task%2C%20and%20each%20task%20is%20one%20recording.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20contractors%20have%20recorded%20an%20audio%20file%2C%20they%20upload%20it%20to%20a%20Scale%20AI%20contributor%20platform%20and%20transcribe%20it%20manually%2C%20with%20the%20Grasslands%20document%20asking%20for%20filler%20words%20such%20as%20%E2%80%9Cuh%E2%80%9D%20to%20be%20left%20in.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20someone%20has%20a%20slight%20pause%2C%20we%20should%20include%20a%20comma%2C%20even%20if%20grammatically%20that%20comma%20is%20incorrect%2C%E2%80%9D%20one%20of%20the%20contractors%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELarge%20language%20models%20require%20vast%20amounts%20of%20quality%20data%20to%20improve.%20Recreating%20real-world%20scenarios%2C%20such%20as%20natural-sounding%20conversations%20between%20people%2C%20is%20one%20way%20to%20generate%20suitable%20data%20to%20feed%20into%20those%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223b815243-2da0-4172-9f8f-c7ff012f22f2%5C%22%3ETraining%20Grok%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EProject%20Xylophone%20is%20an%20example%20of%20a%20larger%20push%20by%20AI%20companies%20to%20inject%20personality%20into%20their%20AIs%20and%20stand%20out%20in%20an%20increasingly%20crowded%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20reported%20last%20month%20that%20Meta%20ran%20a%20project%20via%20Scale%20AI%20asking%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-ai-chatbot-training-scaleai-safe-flirty-leaked-documents-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egig%20workers%20training%20its%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20adopt%20different%20personas%2C%20such%20as%20%E2%80%9Ca%20wise%20and%20mystical%20wizard%26quot%3B%20or%20a%20%26quot%3Bhyper-excited%20music%20theory%20student.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%E2%80%99s%20Sam%20Altman%20said%20in%20late%20April%20that%20the%20latest%20GPT-4o%20had%20become%20%E2%80%9Ctoo%20sycophant-y%20and%20annoying%2C%E2%80%9D%20prompting%20a%20reset%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-changes-nice-openai-overly-complimentary-model-tweak-supportive-personality-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emake%20its%20replies%20more%20natural%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ExAI%20has%20marketed%20Grok%20as%20a%20politically%20edgier%20chatbot%20compared%20to%20what%20Musk%20has%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-gemini-woke-images-ai-chatbot-criticism-controversy-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cwoke%E2%80%9D%20rivals%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20training%20methods%20that%20sometimes%20lean%20heavily%20on%20right-wing%20or%20contrarian%20views%2C%20BI%20previously%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxai-grok-training-bias-woke-idealogy-2025-02%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Alongside%20xAI%E2%80%99s%20outsourced%20work%2C%20the%20company%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxai-elon-musk-hiring-ramp-up-data-annotators-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehundreds%20of%20in-house%20%E2%80%9CAI%20tutors%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20plans%20to%20hire%20thousands%20more%2C%20BI%20reported%20in%20February%2C%20showing%20the%20huge%20human%20effort%20involved%2