lliams-Lindo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ECareer%20coach%20Patrice%20Williams-Lindo%20has%20three%20daughters%20who%20are%20about%20to%20enter%20the%20workforce.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20advises%20them%20to%20craft%20impactful%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20and%20emphasizes%20intentional%20reputation%20management.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20also%20encourages%20being%20a%20go-to%20person%20and%20finding%20personal%20work%20styles%20for%20career%20success.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcareernomad.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPatrice%20Williams-Lindo%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20a%2052-year-old%20career%20coach%20in%20the%20Bronx%2C%20New%20York.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20the%20CEO%20of%20Career%20Nomad%2C%20a%20career%20pivot%20coaching%20consultancy.%20After%20watching%20too%20many%20brilliant%20professionals%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20Black%20women%20%E2%80%94%20be%20underutilized%20or%20erased%2C%20I%20started%20Career%20Nomad%20to%20help%20people%20rebrand%2C%20get%20visible%2C%20and%20walk%20into%20rooms%20that%20truly%20recognize%20their%20worth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20over%2020%20years%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-break-into-management-consulting-career-coach-mbb-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emanagement%20consulting%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20workforce%20transformation%2C%20and%20leadership%20development%20at%20firms%20like%20Deloitte%20and%20KPMG.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20remember%20when%20I%20was%20in%20college%2C%20I'd%20get%20the%20Sunday%20newspaper%20and%20mark%20all%20the%20jobs%20I%20wanted%20to%20apply%20for.%20Then%20I'd%20type%20up%20my%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20on%20a%20computer%20and%20mail%20it%20off%2C%20hoping%20for%20a%20callback.%20Times%20have%20changed%2C%20and%20so%20have%20the%20measures%20we%20have%20to%20take%20to%20land%20our%20next%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2286874474-72f5-467c-89d4-9b95aa67e201%5C%22%3EI%20have%20three%20college-aged%20daughters%20who%20will%20soon%20be%20looking%20for%20work%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20my%20daughters%20graduated%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20daughter%20Jordanne%20just%20graduated%20with%20a%20bachelor's%20in%20business%20administration%2C%20specializing%20in%20healthcare%20administration.%20My%20youngest%20daughter%2C%20Natalya%2C%20also%20graduated%20this%20year%20with%20a%20BA%20in%20religion%20and%20philosophy%2C%20specializing%20in%20social%20change%20and%20gender%20studies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20finding%20jobs%20and%20building%20their%20careers%2C%20here's%20the%20advice%20I%20give%20them%20and%20would%20give%20any%20job%20seeker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228b04eaac-5db1-452a-9050-32901e5994e1%5C%22%3E1.%20Write%20an%20impactful%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20competitive%20for%20a%20job%2C%20your%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20must%20clearly%20state%20what%20you've%20done%20and%20what%20you%20can%20do.%20The%20hiring%20manager%20should%20think%2C%20%3Cem%3Eshe%20is%20a%20tastemaker%2C%20a%20changemaker%2C%20and%20results-driven%3C%2Fem%3E%20after%20reading%20your%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20looking%20at%20my%20daughters'%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%2C%20I%20make%20sure%20they%20have%20an%20impact.%20Even%20though%20their%20jobs%20may%20have%20been%20work-study%20or%20as%20RAs%2C%20there's%20still%20a%20way%20for%20them%20to%20quantify%20what%20they're%20doing.%20They%20shouldn't%20just%20talk%20about%20the%20tasks%20they%20performed%20but%20also%20about%20the%20results%20and%20outcomes%20they%20drove.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20strengthens%20your%20internal%20voice.%20If%20you're%20part%20of%20a%20team%20and%20accomplished%20something%20together%2C%20you%20can%20still%20say%20that.%20For%20example%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20part%20of%20a%20team%20that%20created%20a%20training%20that%20impacted%2080%2C000%20people%26quot%3B%20is%20much%20better%20than%20%26quot%3BI%20created%20a%20course.%26quot%3B%20I%20always%20have%20my%20daughters%20thinking%2C%20%3Cem%3Ewhat's%20the%20so%20what%3C%2Fem%3E%20about%20anything%20they%20put%20on%20their%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20tell%20them%20to%20think%20of%20their%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20as%20prime%20real%20estate.%20What's%20the%20highlight%20of%20what%20you've%20done%20so%20far%3F%20What%20different%20skills%20do%20you%20have%20that%20won't%20necessarily%20jump%20out%3F%20If%20you're%20an%20RA%2C%20you%20might%20be%20well-versed%20in%20conflict%20resolution.%20Say%20that.%20If%20you're%20having%20conversations%20between%20leadership%20and%20students%2C%20you%20might%20be%20a%20good%20mediator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2206db700c-a66a-44ac-90cc-9b1b44827bda%5C%22%3E2.%20Be%20intentional%20with%20your%20reputation%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-not-to-share-online-during-job-search-career-coach-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eyour%20reputation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it's%20not%20just%20how%20you%20show%20up%20at%20work%20or%20how%20you%20dress%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20what%20you're%20talking%20about%20and%20how%20you%20show%20up%20both%20virtually%20and%20in%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20are%20you%20reacting%20to%3F%20What%20are%20you%20speaking%20about%3F%20What%20networks%20are%20you%20in%3F%20You%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20your%20reputation%2C%20whether%20you're%20building%20it%20or%20maintaining%20it%2C%20is%20intentional.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20I%20tell%20my%20graduating%20daughters%3A%20Yes%2C%20use%20LinkedIn%2C%20TikTok%2C%20and%20X%20%E2%80%94%20do%20your%20thing%2C%20but%20be%20cautious%20about%20how%20you're%20showing%20up.%20If%20you're%20suited%20and%20booted%20on%20LinkedIn%20but%20a%20social%20media%20search%20shows%20you%20lying%20on%20the%20beach%2C%20drunk%20(God%20forbid)%2C%20that%20can%20leave%20an%20impression.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20don't%20want%20to%20miss%20out%20on%20an%20opportunity%20simply%20because%20a%20snap%20judgment%20was%20made.%20And%20it's%20not%20just%20appearance%20%E2%80%94%20people%20might%20look%20up%20where%20you%20live%2C%20who%20you're%20connected%20to%2C%20or%20even%20your%20beliefs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22271b3381-9221-4239-af3b-b7e4ee11430e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Be%20a%20go-to%20person%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20all%20my%20roles%20over%20the%20years%2C%20I've%20often%20been%20an%20early%20adopter.%20When%20I%20worked%20in%20a%20hospital%20setting%2C%20anytime%20there%20were%20tech%20upgrades%2C%20I'd%20raise%20my%20hand%20to%20learn%20them%20and%20then%20bring%20that%20information%20back%20to%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20positioned%20me%20as%20someone%20with%20a%20finger%20on%20the%20pulse.%20I%20found%20that%20by%20getting%20information%20early%2C%20I%20had%20time%20to%20understand%20it%2C%20share%20it%2C%20and%20even%20shape%20how%20it%20was%20used.%20It's%20a%20great%20way%20to%20set%20yourself%20apart%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20as%20someone%20who%20consumes%20information%20but%20as%20someone%20who%20contributes%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20advice%20is%20to%20position%20yourself%20as%20a%20go-to%20person%20and%20a%20thought%20leader.%20By%20showing%20up%20early%2C%20you%20can%20help%20shape%20the%20direction%20and%20impact%20you%20want%20to%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223b0f11fb-d464-43b2-bcde-85111376c791%5C%22%3E4.%20Find%20what%20works%20for%20you%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20recently%20listening%20to%20a%20conversation%20about%20how%20Gen%20Z%20likes%20to%20watch%20TV%20or%20have%20music%20playing%20in%20the%20background%20while%20working.%20The%20rhetoric%20was%20that%20they%20were%20distracted.%20I%20remember%20thinking%2C%20no%2C%20it%20depends.%20You%20can%20have%20the%20TV%20playing%2C%2