rograms%20can%20offer%20more%20networking%20and%20job%20opportunities%20than%20their%20European%20counterparts%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESitting%20on%20the%20decision%20to%20apply%20for%20too%20long%20may%20hurt%20a%20candidate's%20acceptance%20chances.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Scott%20Edinburgh%2C%20a%20Boston-based%20MBA%20admissions%20consultant.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20launched%20an%20admissions%20consulting%20business%20in%202008%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20a%20family%20business%20that%20I%20run%20with%20my%20sister.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20international%20students%2C%20and%20they%20sometimes%20make%20up%20half%20our%20clients%20for%20the%20year.%20Our%20reach%20matches%20what%20many%20schools%20are%20seeing.%20There%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20interest%20from%20India%20and%20China%2C%20as%20well%20as%20growing%20numbers%20in%20Europe%2C%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20and%20some%20countries%20in%20Africa.%20For%20MBA%20programs%2C%20most%20students%20are%20in%20their%20mid-%20to%20late%2020s%20and%20have%20some%20years%20of%20work%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20offer%20guidance%20for%20universities%20in%20Europe%20and%20some%20other%20places%2C%20but%20there%20are%20still%20some%20unique%20features%20about%20pursuing%20an%20MBA%20in%20the%20US.%20An%20MBA%20as%20a%20course%20is%20more%20popular%20in%20the%20US%20than%20Europe%20and%20it%20opens%20up%20more%20networking%20opportunities%2C%20and%20the%20degree%20holds%20a%20bit%20more%20value.%20US%20programs%20are%20also%20stronger%20from%20a%20recruiting%20and%20job%20standpoint.%20It%20also%20comes%20down%20to%20where%20you%20want%20to%20establish%20yourself.%20If%20you%20want%20to%20live%20in%20the%20US%2C%20there's%20no%20better%20way%20to%20do%20it%20than%20to%20study%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20uncertainty%20surrounding%20US%20immigration%20policies%2C%20we've%20been%20getting%20questions%20about%20studying%20and%20working%20in%20the%20US%20and%20seeing%20some%20students%20apply%20to%20European%20schools%20instead.%20Still%2C%20there%20are%20a%20couple%20of%20reasons%20tons%20of%20students%20are%20still%20keen%20on%20pursuing%20an%20MBA%20in%20the%20US%20and%20why%20I%20recommend%20they%20apply%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b295787e-704d-4e15-8531-57a09dc47756%5C%22%3ESchools%20are%20working%20hard%20to%20keep%20international%20students%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20getting%20questions%20about%20the%20US%20being%20open%20to%20accepting%20international%20students%20and%20the%20risks%20of%20studying%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20over%201.1%20million%20international%20students%20in%20the%20US%20right%20now%2C%20and%20they're%20not%20all%20being%20kicked%20out%20and%20told%20to%20leave.%20There's%20a%20lot%20of%20hesitation%20among%20some%20international%20students%20about%20their%20ability%20to%20show%20up%20on%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20we're%20seeing%20from%20talking%20with%20deans%20and%20councils%20is%20that%20schools%20are%20doing%20a%20lot%20so%20that%20they%20can%20have%20their%20international%20students.%20These%20students%20make%20up%20a%20large%20percentage%20of%20the%20class%20at%20top%20business%20schools.%20Their%20legal%20teams%20are%20quite%20strong%2C%20and%20we've%20seen%20a%20lot%20of%20court%20interventions%20to%20uphold%20the%20rights%20and%20opportunities%20for%20international%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20seems%20like%20there's%20an%20issue%20now%2C%20it's%20probably%20going%20to%20work%20itself%20out.%20People%20hesitating%20means%20there%20are%20fewer%20applicants%2C%20which%20means%20you're%20more%20likely%20to%20get%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fe4ade65-dd76-48ce-b6c3-b622a3a5dd63%5C%22%3EYou're%20not%20entering%20the%20job%20market%20now%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20are%20worried%20about%20the%20job%20market%20not%20being%20great%2C%20and%20they're%20reading%20jobs%20reports%20that%20are%20coming%20out%20from%20these%20schools.%20We%20tell%20them%20you're%20not%20applying%20to%20apply%20for%20a%20job%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThings%20are%20cyclical.%20If%20you're%20applying%20to%20business%20school%20in%202025%20and%20graduating%20in%202028%2C%20that's%20three%20years%20from%20now.%20The%20chances%20are%20that%20the%20job%20market%20will%20not%20be%20in%20the%20same%20place%20three%20years%20from%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%20is%20the%20absolute%20best%20time%20to%20apply.%20This%20will%20be%20the%20best%20round%20in%20the%20span%20of%20many%20rounds%20that%20I've%20seen%20as%20far%20as%20acceptance%20rates%20go.%20The%20market%20is%20not%20great%20job-wise%20wise%20and%20you%20can%20spend%20that%20time%20educating%20yourself.%20You%20won't%20be%20missing%20out%20on%20huge%20promotions%2C%20huge%20raises%2C%20and%20new%20jobs.%20By%20the%20time%20you%20graduate%2C%20things%20may%20start%20to%20improve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ef913b07-3535-4db9-adce-1b1d9bd45541%5C%22%3EMBAs%20are%20time-bound%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20job%20market%20and%20political%20situation%20add%20an%20element%20of%20risk%2C%20but%20those%20who%20are%20looking%20to%20get%20ahead%20will%20find%20a%20way%20to%20succeed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStudents%20often%20forget%20that%20the%20MBA%20is%20a%20time-bound%20program%2C%20and%20waiting%20too%20long%20to%20apply%20while%20the%20situation%20clears%20up%20might%20make%20it%20too%20difficult%20to%20get%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUniversities%20prefer%20those%20in%20their%20mid-%20to%20late%2020s%20because%20they%20are%20easier%20to%20place%20into%20jobs%20and%20because%20they%20want%20cohorts%20to%20mesh%20well.%20The%20median%20number%20of%20years%20of%20experience%20is%20five%2C%20and%20as%20you%20go%20further%20down%20the%20bell%20curve%2C%20there%20are%20just%20fewer%20and%20fewer%20spots%20that%20are%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnless%20you%20are%20in%20your%20early%2020s%2C%20you%20could%20be%20shooting%20yourself%20in%20the%20foot%20by%20delaying%20by%20one%20or%20two%20years.%20The%20fear%20of%20what%20might%20happen%20from%20a%20policy%20standpoint%20becomes%20irrelevant%20if%20you%20don't%20get%20into%20a%20program%20in%20a%20future%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20international%20graduate%20students%20in%20the%20US%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20sgoel%40businessinsider.com.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finternational-mba-students-applying-us-universities-immigration-business-school-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749112045000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F684138a09d73a0031e8de7aa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finternational-mba-students-applying-us-universities-immigration-business-school-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Scott%20Edinburgh%2C%20an%20MBA%20admissions%20consultant%2C%20said%20that%20there%20are%20a%20couple%20of%20reasons%20why%20he%20is%20still%20advising%20clients%20to%20apply%20to%20US%20universities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sgoel%40insider.com%20(Shubhangi%20Goel)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finternational-mba-students-applying-us-universities-immigration-business-school-2025-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Aankhon%20Ki%20Gustaakhiyan%E2%80%99%20teaser%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749112002000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-121644004%2Cimgsize-26354.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Faankhon-ki-gustaakhiyan-teaser-vikrant-massey-and-shanaya-kapoor-explore-a-fragile-romance-born-of