0a%20yearslong%20battle.%20They've%20been%20loyally%20listening%20to%20re-recorded%20%26quot%3BTaylor's%20Version%26quot%3B%20songs%20and%20abstaining%20from%20listening%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bstolen%26quot%3B%20versions%20since%202019%20to%20avoid%20enriching%20mega-manager%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-feuds-then-now-enemies-haters-2023-8%23taylor-swift-spoke-out-against-scooter-braun-when-he-acquired-her-masters-in-2019-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EScooter%20Braun%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20then%20Shamrock%20Holdings%2C%20from%20whom%20Swift%20made%20the%20purchase%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20another%20prescient%20marketing%20move%20from%20the%20megastar%3A%20Fans%20are%20joking%20that%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-taylor-swift-fans-spend-concerts-eras-tour-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Espending%20on%20the%20Eras%20Tour%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20for%20many%20was%20in%20the%20hundreds%20or%20thousands%2C%20functioned%20as%20a%20form%20of%20GoFundMe%20for%20Swift%20to%20make%20the%20purchase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrystal%20Haryanto%2C%20who%20started%20a%20course%20on%20Swift%20at%20UC%20Berkeley%20and%20is%20the%20author%20of%20the%20upcoming%20book%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Glory%20of%20Giving%20Everything%2C%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20star's%20business%20model%2C%20said%20the%20letter%20Swift%20wrote%20did%20more%20than%20express%20gratitude.%20It%20%26quot%3Breminds%20fans%20that%20they%20have%20equity%20in%20the%20music%2C%26quot%3B%20though%20not%20legally%2C%20of%20course.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20a%20marketing%20perspective%2C%20presenting%20this%20milestone%20as%20a%20joint%20effort%20is%20conducive%20to%20sales%20of%20future%20albums%2C%26quot%3B%20Haryanto%20said.%20%26quot%3BFans%20are%20motivated%20to%20keep%20listening%20to%20her%20music%20because%20such%20actions%20appear%20to%20have%20a%20measurable%20impact%20on%20Swift's%20well-being%E2%80%94the%20dream%20of%20any%20fan%20toward%20their%20favorite%20person.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Kerry%20Weber%2C%20a%2046-year-old%20Swiftie%20in%20marketing%20who%20attended%20the%20Reputation%20tour%20and%20multiple%20dates%20of%20the%20Eras%20Tour%2C%20said%20that%20Swift%20made%20several%20%26quot%3Bgenius%26quot%3B%20marketing%20moves%20in%20the%20lead-up%20to%20the%20masters%20acquisition%2C%20such%20as%20the%20re-recordings%20and%20adding%20new%20sets%20to%20the%20tour%20after%20the%20wildly%20successful%20concert%20film%20was%20released.%20Weber%20said%20that%20the%20sentiment%20among%20the%20%26quot%3Bhaters%26quot%3B%20was%20that%20Swift%20milked%20money%20from%20her%20fans%20%E2%80%94%20something%20she%20disputes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20got%20something%20in%20return%20is%20how%20I%20look%20at%20it.%20I%20got%20to%20go%20to%20London%20with%20my%20daughter%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20and%20that%20was%20amazing.%20I%20don't%20care%2C%20she%20can%20have%20my%20money%20just%20for%20that%20alone%2C%26quot%3B%20Weber%2C%20who%20estimated%20that%20she%20spent%20a%20few%20thousand%20dollars%20on%20a%20London%20trip%20for%20the%20Eras%20Tour%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20if%20that%20money%20bought%20back%20her%20masters%2C%20I%20think%20it's%20fantastic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaryanto%20said%20that%20bridging%20the%20gap%20with%20fans%20has%20always%20been%20%26quot%3Bfoundational%26quot%3B%20to%20Swift's%20branding%20strategy.%20She%20described%20it%20as%20akin%20to%20attracting%20repeat%20customers%20in%20retail%20%E2%80%94%20it%20curates%20customers%20who%20not%20only%20come%20back%2C%20but%20get%20even%20more%20satisfaction%20from%20supporting%20the%20brand%20as%20a%20whole.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20know%20that%20the%20money%20I%20spent%20at%20a%20concert%20was%20going%20to%20something%20like%20this%20and%20was%20going%20to%20this%20project%20that%20I%20think%20will%20hopefully%20also%20change%20things%20for%20other%20artists%20a