arisaraa%2C%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20oldest%20e-waste%20recyclers.%20That%20experience%20changed%20the%20course%20of%20my%20life.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENandan%20spent%20two%20years%20working%20with%20a%20waste%20management%20company%20in%20Bilbao%2C%20Spain%2C%20rotating%20through%20procurement%2C%20logistics%2C%20operations%2C%20and%20dismantling.%20That%20global%20exposure%20helped%20him%20build%20a%20solid%20foundation%20for%20Hulladek%20Recycling%20when%20he%20returned%20to%20India%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHulladek%20is%20a%20Hungarian%20word%20for%20%E2%80%98waste%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20nod%20to%20the%20universal%20nature%20of%20the%20problem%20we%E2%80%99re%20trying%20to%20solve.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20always%20seen%20waste%20not%20as%20a%20burden%2C%20but%20as%20a%20resource.%20That%20mindset%2C%20alongside%20the%20growing%20urgency%20of%20climate%20action%20and%20sustainable%20industry%2C%20cemented%20my%20belief%20that%20waste%20management%20is%20the%20next%20big%20revolution%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Nandan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20started%20as%20a%20belief%20soon%20turned%20into%20a%20movement.%20Hulladek%20Recycling%20stepped%20in%20to%20tackle%20a%20gap%20that%E2%80%99s%20often%20overlooked%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20waste%20story%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cstrong%3Ee-waste%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20day%2C%20our%20old%20phones%2C%20broken%20chargers%2C%20defunct%20laptops%2C%20and%20discarded%20appliances%20quietly%20pile%20up.%20While%20they%20may%20seem%20like%20junk%2C%20these%20electronics%20are%20actually%20a%20goldmine%2C%20quite%20literally.%20They%20contain%20valuable%20materials%20like%20copper%2C%20aluminum%2C%20silver%2C%20and%20even%20g