20a%20practice%20that%20distinguishes%20us%20from%20informal%20%3Cem%3Ekabadiwala%3C%2Fem%3Es%20(scrap%20dealers)%2C%20who%20are%20often%20confused%20with%20formal%20recyclers%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShreya%20says%20what%20makes%20Hulladek%20unique%20is%20not%20just%20its%20mission%20but%20its%20workforce%2C%20which%20is%20predominantly%20led%20by%20women.%20%E2%80%9CWith%20an%20average%20employee%20age%20of%2027%2C%20we%20strive%20to%20be%20innovative%20in%20the%20waste%20management%20industry%2C%20and%20our%20gender%20diversity%20is%20unparalleled%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shreya%20beams%20with%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHulladek%E2%80%99s%20work%20is%20rooted%20in%20an%20apparent%20belief%3A%20change%20begins%20with%20awareness.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20the%20organisation%20has%20built%20a%20formidable%20logistics%20network%20backed%20by%20intention%20and%20community%20engagement.%20With%20more%20than%2060%20collection%20centres%20spread%20across%20cities%20like%20Surat%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Coimbatore%2C%20Jaipur%2C%20Delhi%2C%20and%20Agartala%2C%20Hulladek%20conducts%20over%20500%20awareness%20sessions%20each%20year%E2%80%94each%20one%20an%20attempt%20to%20shift%20mindsets%20and%20turn%20passive%20consumers%20into%20conscious%20participants%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20e-waste%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Eastern%20India%2C%20their%20presence%20is%20especially%20significant.%20In%20cities%20like%20Kolkata%2C%20Hulladek%20has%20installed%20nearly%20500%20e-waste%20bins%2C%20not%20just%20as%20collection%20points%20but%20as%20visible%2C%20everyday%20reminders%20that%20electronic%20waste%20is%20real%20and%20needs%20attention.%20These%20bins%2C%20placed%20in%20schools%2C%20offices%2C%20and%20public%20spaces%2C%20have%20become%20quiet%20markers%20of%20a%20larger%20mission%3A%20to%20make%20e-waste%20visible%2C%20understood%2C%20and%20acted%20upon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20a%20smooth%20path.%20The%20road%20to%20awareness%2C%20as%20Priyasha%20Singhania%20shares%2C%20has%20been%20long%20and%20layered.%20%E2%80%9CAwareness%20about%20biodegradable%20and%20non-biodegradable%20waste%20was%20high%2C%20but%20e-waste%20was%20being%20overlooked%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20Executive%20Vice%20President%2C%20Branding%20and%20Communication.%20Her%20words%20reflect%20a%20national%20blind%20spot%E2%80%94a%20collective%20unawareness%20of%20the%20toxins%20hiding%20in%20our%20broken%20gadgets%20and%20discarded%20electronics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-4-1748957985.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hulladek%20has%20diverted%20over%2015%20million%20kilograms%20of%20waste%20from%20landfills.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-4-1748957985.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-4-1748957985-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-4-1748957985-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-4-1748957985-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-4-1748957985-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-443728%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHulladek%20has%20diverted%20over%2015%20million%20kilograms%20of%20waste%20from%20landfills.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHulladek%20recognised%20early%20on%20that%20ignoring%20this%20problem%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20an%20option.%20The%20risks%20were%20too%20great%2C%20and%20the%20silence%20too%20loud.%20So%20they%20built%20something%20meaningful%E2%80%94systems%20that%20not%20only%20enable%20safe%20recycling%20but%20also%20recover%20valuable%20materials%20like%20gold%2C%20copper%2C%20and%20aluminium%2C%20returning%20them%20to%20the%20production%20cycle.%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20created%20a%20model%20that%20protects%20both%20human%20health%20and%20natural%20resources%20while%20also%20reshaping%20how%20India%20thinks%20about%20its%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20deep-rooted%20challenge%20Hulladek%20Recycling%20continues%20to%20confront%20is%20the%20perception%20that%20equates%20recyclers%20with%20local%20scrap%20dealers.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20misconception%20that%20undermines%20the%20scale%20and%20seriousness%20of%20their%20work.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20often%20mistake%20us%20for%20just%20another%20scrap%20dealer%2C%20whereas%20we%20operate%20with%20government-approved%20systems%20and%20documentation%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Priyasha.%20Changing%20this%20mindset%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20easy%2C%20but%20Hulladek%20has%20met%20it%20head-on.%20They%E2%80%99ve%20worked%20relentlessly%20through%20persistent%20educational%20outreach%20and%20years%20of%20steady%20community%20engagement%20to%20rebuild%20trust%20and%20establish%20credibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHulladek%20has%20joined%20hands%20with%20state%20pollution%20control%20boards%20in%20Punjab%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Andaman%2C%20Assam%2C%20Nagaland%2C%20and%20Gujarat%20to%20amplify%20this%20effort.%20These%20partnerships%20are%20not%20symbolic%E2%80%94they%20serve%20as%20the%20foundation%20for%20grassroots%20change.%20By%20training%20board%20members%20and%20sensitising%20citizens%2C%20the%20company%20is%20helping%20communities%20understand%20what%E2%80%99s%20at%20stake%20and%20equipping%20them%20with%20the%20tools%20to%20take%20meaningful%20action%20against%20unsafe%20e-waste%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Hulladek%20manages%20e-waste%20collection%20for%20over%20300%20contract-based%20clients%2C%20including%20schools%2C%20colleges%2C%20and%20corporations%2C%20each%20one%20a%20step%20closer%20to%20a%20cleaner%2C%20safer%20system.%20Among%20them%20is%20GTPL%20KCPL%2C%20a%20major%20player%20managing%20a%20staggering%2040%20lakh%20cable%20TV%20boxes.%20Their%20director%2C%20Ankit%20Agarwal%2C%20acknowledges%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20partnership%2C%20further%20underlining%20Hulladek%E2%80%99s%20growing%20role%20in%20shaping%20responsible%20e-waste%20management%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-5-1748958138.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hulladek%20has%20more%20than%2060%20collection%20centres%20spread%20across%20cities%20like%20Surat%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Coimbatore%2C%20Jaipur%2C%20Delhi%2C%20and%20Agartala.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-5-1748958138.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-5-1748958138-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-5-1748958138-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-5-1748958138-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-5-1748958138-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-443731%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHulladek%20has%20more%20than%2060%20collection%20centres%20spread%20across%20cities%20like%20Surat%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Coimbatore%2C%20Jaipur%2C%20Delhi%2C%20and%20Agartala.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20we%20struggled%20with%20the%20proper%20disposal%20of%20our%20cable%20boxes.%20Partnering%20with%20Hulladek%20was%20both%20a%20moral%20imperative%20and%20a%20practical%20step.%20While%20the%20local%20selling%20methods%20to%20%3Cem%3Ekabadiwala%3C%2Fem%3Es%20were%20questionable%2C%20we%20had%20no%20alternative%20until%20we%20partnered%20with%20Hulladek%2C%20which%20is%20committed%20to%20ethical%20and%20legal%20disposal%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20explaining%20the%20benefits%20of%20their%20e-waste%20partnership%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20decision%20was%20driven%20by%20a%20conviction%20to%20protect%20the%20ecosystem%20and%20uphold%20our%20corporate%20social%20responsibility.%20Apart%20from%20financial%20gain%20from%20selling%20scrap%2C%20we%20now%20have%20assurance%20that%20our%20e-waste%20is%20managed%20ethically.%20Recycling%20ensures%20that%20resources%20that%20would%20have%20ended%20up%20in%20landfills%20are%20reused.%20As%20companies%20become%20more%20aware%2C%20these%20efforts%20encourage%20a%20more%20sustainable%20business%20environment%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20true%20power%20of%20waste%20lies%20in%20what%20we%20teach%20the%20next%20generation%20to%20do%20with%20it%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20Hulladek%20Recycling%20has%20helped%20divert%20more%20than%2025%20million%20kilograms%20of%20waste%20away%20from%20landfills%2C%20polluted%20waterways%2C%20and%20unsafe%20dumping%20grounds.%20This%20includes%20an%20astonishing%2015%20million%20kilograms%20of%20e-waste%E2%80%94a%20mix%20of%20everyday%20items%20like%20remote%20controls%2C%20hair%20straighteners%2C%20and%20large-scale%20appliances%20such%20as%20transformers%20and%20ATMs.%20Behind%20every%20kilogram%20is%20a%20moment%20of%20choice%3A%20to%20discard%20thoughtlessly%2C%20or%20to%20recycle%20responsibly.%20Hulladek%20is%20working%20to%20ensure%20that%20more%20people%20choose%20the%20latter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20life%20gives%20you%20lemonade%2C%20we%20make%20lemons.%20That%E2%80%99s%20recycling%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nandan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20numbers%20reflect%20growth%2C%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20more%20resounding%20success%20lies%20in%20its%20purpose.%20In%20the%20last%20financial%20year%2C%20Hulladek%20reported%20an%20annual%20turnover%20of%20%E2%82%B920%20crore%2C%20with%20a%20profit%20margin%20of%20at%20least%20five%20percent.%20Yet%20for%20founder%20Nandan%2C%20impact%20is%20not%20just%20financial%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20transformational.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20such%20transformation%20took%20shape%20through%20a%20partnership%20with%20Calcutta%20International%20School.%20By%20directly%20engaging%20students%2C%20Hulladek%20helped%20bridge%20the%20gap%20between%20technology%20use%20and%20environmental%20responsibility.%20The%20results%20were%20powerful.%20Tina%20shares%2C%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fem%3EOur%20students%20have%20evolved%20beyond%20mere%20technology%20consumers%3B%20they%20are%20consumers%20with%20a%20conscience%2C%20a%20voice%2C%20and%20a%20responsibility.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBecause%20sometimes%2C%20real%20change%20begins%20not%20in%20boardrooms%20or%20factories%20but%20in%20classrooms%2C%20conversations%2C%20and%20the%20small%20decisions%20we%20make%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Leila%20Badyari%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749040200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-1-1748957830.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D443701%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hulladek%20Recycling%20began%20with%20a%20simple%20idea%3A%20treat%20e-waste%20not%20as%20junk%2C%20but%20as%20a%20responsibility.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20helped%20divert%2015%20million%20kg%20of%20electronic%20waste%20from%20landfills%20while%20quietly%20building%20awareness%20in%20schools%2C%20homes%2C%20and%20offices%20across%20Indi